            <h3 data-uuid="b1fcbea17e464d01bc165442574fdb39">Part 2: Write an Analytical Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="8ce1ba7789584ee3a32bd40efdd7bd7c">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="6d3dbfd2c4e042abae5d0d3c31c4f510">In the late 1800s rapid
                industrialization in the United States led many people to move to American
                cities. Among these people were millions of Europeans. Some fled religious or
                political persecution in their countries of origin. Many came to find jobs. Most
                settled in large cities like New York City, Chicago, and Boston, where most
                manufacturing jobs were located.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="f0efa02c20d24d39b52db9ffc64c8f0e">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="7ed297b6fc934c5fb6a15f4257e22152"></p>
            <p data-uuid="0a82c2096d1d493ea32a9b93128251b1">Immigrants to the United States often
                arrived with little money and few possessions. Yet they had to find a way to
                establish a life. What challenges faced immigrants who settled in Americaâ€™s
                urban areas? What opportunities did they encounter? Write an analytical essay
                that addresses these questions.</p>
            <p data-uuid="68196b83ba334b5b882d440ea8304c4a"></p>
            <p data-uuid="afbe397c662542ecb0abfcc8859629b7">Complete the following steps as you
                plan and compose your essay.</p>
            <ol start="1" type="1" data-uuid="2e7a0e54992e4aecad57c4b4d67375c7">
                <li data-uuid="6ad44fdd8b5f46f38a3d08736b5bf741">Review
                    your notes and sources before you start writing.</li>
                <li data-uuid="e6121945e4af41b697c649c29e044f95">Use at
                    least <i>two</i> of the sources in Part
                    1, and develop the topic with relevant, well-chosen text evidence from the
                    documents.</li>
                <li data-uuid="e79e9010dac84f8eae5f4f3a170cb990">Cite
                    specific text evidence from each of the two sources in your response.</li>
                <li data-uuid="818e7c234eba4f40a0f448e8fb379d43">Plan your
                    essay so that it includes an introduction, several body paragraphs, and a
                    concluding paragraph.</li>
                <li data-uuid="f6c264f804ed4338adbf7c905cac4146">Organize your essay in a clear and logical way that links evidence and important details to your main topic.</li>
                <li data-uuid="ac892bfb36be4520844fd700cb36eb23">Write a conclusion that sums up your ideas and supports the information you present.<br />
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
